menuItems.name: Tripple Dipper
menuItems.description: Why choose one when you can choose three? Select three appetizers and enjoy! Served with dipping sauces.

menuItems.description: Your chip’s favorite dip for over 25 years. Original with beef. Served with chips & salsa.

menuItems.name: Fried Pickles
menuItems.description: Served with house-made ranch.
